overview: Rock + Symphony = Jian Cui's latest live album! 　　On one side is the ego and on the other is the collective consciousness. 　　One man's roar, and a flamboyant rendition of a crowd. 　　When rock meets symphony, how does it spark? 　　Let Ken Choi tell you the answer. 　　--Cui Jian "Rock Symphony" live album
title: Rock Symphony Live Concert
